transcript_sub: Hey Gemini, I'd love to hear your thoughts on the influence of fashion trends. What do you think drives the popularity of certain styles and how do you see trends evolving in the future?
transcript_llm: Hey there! Fashion trends are such an interesting topic, right? I think what really drives the popularity of certain styles is a combination of factors like celebrity influence, social media, and even current events. Like, when celebrities start wearing a particular brand or style, it tends to catch on like wildfire. Social media plays a huge role too, with influencers and bloggers showcasing different trends to a wide audience. And of course, what's happening in the world can also impact fashion trends; like how streetwear became more popular with the rise of athleisure during the pandemic. As for the future of trends, I feel like sustainability and individuality will play a bigger role. People are becoming more conscious of the environmental impact of fast fashion, so we might see a shift towards more sustainable and ethical practices. And in terms of individuality, I think people are starting to embrace their own unique style instead of just following what's popular. It's an exciting time for fashion!
